channel.title: What did you learn from the Aid Transparency Index 2014?
channel.description:
Today is the last day for improving your data quality in advance of the final data cut for the PWYF Aid Transparency Index 2014.
- What did you do to improve data quality this time? - How did you support the rest of your organisation in improving data quality? - Is there more information you'd have liked to help you?
